entry.title: exilon/QuickLib
entry.summary: Quick development library (AutoMapper, LinQ, IOC Dependency Injection, MemoryCache, Scheduled tasks, Json and Yml Config and Options pattern, Serializers, etc) with crossplatform support for Delphi/Firemonkey (Windows,Linux,OSX/IOS/Android) and freepascal (Windows/Linux).
